 8612307, "raw_content": "", "author": "wst4", "created": 1778522968085, "profile_picture": "K15ahGsDhQtO", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "projectarcturus1", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsPkqJst.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/nFdtx6eKwi31.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/N20qD4vvKkaZA3U1.jpeg", "width": 680, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 453}], "blurhash": "UJF}[+r:?^56~V_MxFRj.8SNxaM{%MRkNxM{", "full_resolution": [453, 680]}, "title": "Dems are sooo stupid, went from wanting to kill Nazis to now wanting to elect a REAL one to the Senate. You can't make this shit up! ", "last_comment_created": 1778526777851, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 2, "score_up": 33, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsPkq3EX", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 36, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8612261, "raw_content": "My mother and father are lifelong Democrats. They have never voted for a republican and are deep into TDS range. \n\nOn Mother's Day, we were talking about trips to Seattle. My mother talked about how much she loved going to downtown Seattle and how great it is. The last time she had been there was 10+ years ago. I told her that all of the shops and places that she liked are now closed, abandoned, and infested with the homeless.\n\nHer response was shocking. \"Yeah, we need to understand that's what happens to big cities eventually.\" She would not understand that we don't have to live like that. All we have to do is enforce the laws of the land and hold people accountable. \n\nShe couldn't accept that as an option. \n\nDems would rather let the world burn than do anything to keep the place going or make it better. ", "author": "Duke442games", "created": 1778521232452, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "AnthonyS", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Dems are not aware that there is any alternative", "last_comment_created": 1778523843197, "content": "<p>My mother and father are lifelong Democrats. They have never voted for a republican and are deep into TDS range.</p>\n<p>On Mother's Day, we were talking about trips to Seattle. My mother talked about how much she loved going to downtown Seattle and how great it is. The last time she had been there was 10+ years ago. I told her that all of the shops and places that she liked are now closed, abandoned, and infested with the homeless.</p>\n<p>Her response was shocking. &quot;Yeah, we need to understand that's what happens to big cities eventually.&quot; She would not understand that we don't have to live like that. All we have to do is enforce the laws of the land and hold people accountable.</p>\n<p>She couldn't accept that as an option.</p>\n<p>Dems would rather let the world burn than do anything to keep the place going or make it better.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 36, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "arch